snippet.textDisplay: I can't recommend enough that you guys look at Call of Heroes. It came out in 2016, written and directed by Benny Chang. It's got an incredible plot and characters, but you guys don't care about that. You guys care about the choreography, which is uhhh, top notch. The final fight scene spans the entire village, and has multiple fights happening simultaneously to the point where i'm pretty sure people accidentally switch opponents sometimes. The movie is full of amazing choreography, and you guys should definitely take a look.
